----[ Purpose

	Adds settings to allow the rotation of the cacti.log

----[ Features

	Enable / Disable
	Set number of days to retain old logs

----[ Installation

	Plugin is Plugin Architecture 2.0 only compatible
	To install, place it in your plugin directory in a folder called "logrotate"
	Then login to Cacti, goto Plugin Management and click "Install" next to the plugin's name

	You can then edit the text under Settings >> "Poller" tab
    
